CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771878200
OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FThe Mexican army has killed the drug
OL,7,Flord known as "El Mencho", delivering
OL,8,Fa significant blow to what had become
OL,9,FMexico's most powerful cartel.
OL,11,FEl Mencho, whose real name was Nemesio
OL,12,FRuben Oseguera Cervantes, was leader
OL,13,Fof the Jalisco New Generation Cartel.
OL,15,FOseguera Cervantes was wounded in an
OL,16,Foperation to capture him Sunday in
OL,17,FTapalpa, Jalisco and he died while
OL,18,Fbeing flown to Mexico City,
OL,19,Fauthorities said in a statement.
OL,26,@tD@Drr
