PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771878200
OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FThe state is the base of the cartel
OL,7,Fknown for trafficking huge quantities
OL,8,Fof fentanyl and other drugs to the
OL,9,FUnited States.
OL,11,FDuring the operation, troops came
OL,12,Funder fire and killed four people at
OL,13,Fthe location. Three more people,
OL,14,Fincluding Oseguera Cervantes, were
OL,15,Fwounded and later died, the statement
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
