PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771878200
OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FTwo others were arrested and armoured
OL,7,Fvehicles, rocket launchers and other
OL,8,Farms were seized. Three members of the
OL,9,Farmed forces were wounded and
OL,10,Freceiving medical treatment.
OL,12,FThe killing of the powerful drug lord
OL,13,Fprompted several hours of roadblocks
OL,14,Fwith burning vehicles in Jalisco and
OL,15,Fother states.
OL,17,FSuch tactics are commonly used by the
OL,18,Fcartels to block military operations.
OL,19,FJalisco cancelled school in the state
OL,20,Ffor Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
