OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771878200
OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FVideos circulating on social media
OL,7,Fshowed plumes of smoke billowing over
OL,8,Fthe tourist city of Puerto Vallarta in
OL,9,FJalisco, and people sprinting through
OL,10,Fthe airport of the state's capital in
OL,11,Fpanic.
OL,13,FOn Sunday afternoon, Air Canada
OL,14,Fannounced it was suspending flights to
OL,15,FPuerto Vallarta "due to an ongoing
OL,16,Fsecurity situation" and advised
OL,17,Fcustomers not to go to their airport.
