OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771878200
OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FCanada's embassy in Mexico warned its
OL,7,Fcitizens in Puerto Vallarta to shelter
OL,8,Fin place and generally to keep a low
OL,9,Fprofile in Jalisco. Governor Pablo
OL,10,FLemus told residents to stay at home
OL,11,Fand suspended public transportation.
OL,13,FThe US State Department had offered a
OL,14,Freward of up to $15 million (around
OL,15,F#11.1 million) for information leading
OL,16,Fto the arrest of El Mencho.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
