OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FThe Jalisco New Generation Cartel,
OL,7,Fknown as CJNG, quickly became one of
OL,8,Fthe most powerful and fastest growing
OL,9,Fcriminal organisations in Mexico. In
OL,10,FFebruary, the Trump administration
OL,11,Fdesignated it as a foreign terrorist
OL,12,Forganization.
OL,14,FMexican President Claudia Sheinbaum,
OL,15,Flike her predecessor, has criticised
OL,16,Fthe "kingpin" strategy of previous
OL,17,Fadministrations that took out cartel
OL,18,Fleaders only to trigger explosions of
OL,19,Fviolence as cartels fractured.
