OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FWhile she has remained popular in
OL,7,FMexico, security is a persistent
OL,8,Fconcern and since US President Donald
OL,9,FTrump took office a year ago, she has
OL,10,Fbeen under tremendous pressure to show
OL,11,Fresults against drug trafficking.
OL,13,FThe Jalisco cartel has been one of the
OL,14,Fmost aggressive cartels in its attacks
OL,15,Fon the military ` including on
OL,16,Fhelicopters ` and is a pioneer in
OL,17,Flaunching explosives from drones and
OL,18,Finstalling mines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
