OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771878200
OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FIn 2020, it carried out a spectacular
OL,7,Fassassination attempt with grenades
OL,8,Fand high-powered rifles in the heart
OL,9,Fof Mexico City against the then head
OL,10,Fof the capital's police force and now
OL,11,Ffederal security secretary.
OL,13,FThe DEA considers the cartel to be as
OL,14,Fpowerful as the Sinaloa cartel, one of
OL,15,FMexico's most infamous criminal
OL,16,Fgroups, with a presence in all 50 US
OL,17,Fstates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
