OL,3,CPowerful drug cartel leader 'El
OL,4,CMencho' killed by Mexican army
OL,6,FIt is one of the main suppliers of
OL,7,Fcocaine to the US market and, like the
OL,8,FSinaloa cartel, earns billions from
OL,9,Fthe production of fentanyl and
OL,10,Fmethamphetamines.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FSinaloa, however, has been weakened by
OL,18,Finfighting after the loss of its
OL,19,Fleaders Ismael "El Mayo" Zambada and
OL,20,FJoaquin "El Chapo" Guzman, both in US
OL,21,Fcustody.
